To run type python snake_game.py 

Inputs include, --width, --height, --fullscreen, --exclusive_fullscreen --player_name
width and height: Chooses the width and height of the game screen.
fullscreen: Overrides width and height, sets the width and height based on the screen.
exclusive fullscreen: Self explanatory (resolution depends on the width and height).
player name: Name that is saved with the score in the scores.txt file.